      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation on at least three systematically refined grids with GCI reporting required.",
      "rationale": "Three-level grid refinement study performed; however, GCI values exceed the 2% threshold in near-impeller shear regions, indicating residual discretization error above the required level."
    },
