      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions must match VAD operating envelope including hematocrit range, temperature, and rotational speed within stated tolerances.",
      "rationale": "Benchmark experiments used bovine blood at 40% hematocrit; target VAD operating range extends to 45% hematocrit and higher shear rates not covered in available test data."
